data.name: Oyster Perpetual
data.description: Stainless steel Rolex Oyster Perpetual lady's wristwatch. Round case in stainless steel, screwed caseback, smooth bezel, screw-down crown. Black dial, automatic movement. Applied baton hour marker, applied arabic numerals, stainless steel baton hands. Permanent second hand central. Stainless steel Oyster bracelet signed Rolex, folding clasp in stainless steel signed Rolex. Dial‚ case and movement signed. Very good condition: case glass index and hands in very good condition, bracelet in very good condition, slight scratches of use on the clasp, supericial patina on the case.
